Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.49,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}女王緒方理奈和森川由綺的熱情歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在這裏做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿遙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎麼了  是誰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒死哦  在這裏不能說這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  居然趁人之危
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  買入吧  把十億定金付了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  你來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從經紀人那裏聽說了情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君回去拿東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是心臟的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像之前就不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君又不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…痔瘡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君…是這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心伯父的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術已經定在年後了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  他還年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生也說一定能康復的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的是藤井君哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是家屬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人現在醒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是森川由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是變漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我這副狼狽樣真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋兒子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去取東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是想說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看來是沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的冬彌君就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  經紀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓她走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道我會回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微拖延下時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都會注意到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看她挺忙的  和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓她趕緊回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  由綺小姐…森川小姐不是來見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來看望我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是順便來看望的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都倒下了還色瞇瞇的  你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道伯父是因為什麼住院的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴一輩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從演唱會回去後就發現在門前一直等著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要責備她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是被要求保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間被佔據  自己一個人整晚都在通宵咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊」什麼啊  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒地方去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公寓口被監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼缺勤  為什麼沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  演唱會的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒我也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也為那些同樣的曲子要唱三遍的孩子們想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你  我們受到了多大的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋  …
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手  把招牌弄壞了就得不償失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞掉重新粘補起來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是鬧彆扭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻團輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  勝負什麼的隨他便了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方理奈的天賦  森川由綺的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有能對抗她們的武器這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些FANS對製造出來的專業歌手已經厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今後是外行的時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說教又如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發揮錯地方的話就讓人困擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂一個神崎樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒有打算永遠都去關注她們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矇混過關的  最多只能是兩首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁還沒有出現明顯破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停推出新的歌手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推歌手又不是免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道在櫻團上已經花費了多少錢了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個笨蛋不做點什麼的話  我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  我們就去交涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能見到緒方社長了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪瑙小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放她回公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到她不敢再犯為止  關到倉庫裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  要去海邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感冒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說輸給由綺？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是  在說那種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個無所謂了  已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  遇到了塞車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了  待會再說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有比那個更重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我還要重要的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰利品的收取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是接下來的方針
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天演唱會的入場來看  由綺的未來也定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈也可以看作是有所提高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來年的緒方事務所就是理奈和由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平分秋色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長  今天的課程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  重要的事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈也很忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也許再見不到哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的話我也可以傳話給緒方先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要自己說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出乎意料  這幅畫竟然可以讓你看呆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為這個國家空氣的關係嗎  和倫敦完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是別具一格的了  要變成自己的東西的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是第一次認輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昨天一晚的事情吧  接下來才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調羹  調羹調羹  沒有調羹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勺子  勺子在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  媽媽到哪兒幹什麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好吃飯才會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還是重要的考試時期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你這樣的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井老師也是個好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  要飛嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿遙  阿遙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來了  不睡著怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了阿遙的粥  已經完全治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就出門了  今天不回來了  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微遠足一下也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是聖誕節嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松山瑪瑙小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  讓你監視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又作歌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  幹得不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱唱看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生小姐  如果可以的話  要去echoes喝杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙你好意  但是我接下來還有個地方要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就算了  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  彼此都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話要對藤井君說的話  我可以轉達
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  您是為什麼而來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？  沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為什麼事都沒有  才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱塚小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是筱塚  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭奇  有事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是請回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能叫…  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說  是你叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.01,0:24:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五頁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.33,0:24:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到的東西  會破壞周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.15,0:24:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不在那裏  所以也無從下手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:53.36,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛という形無いもの　とらわれている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:17:00.85,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心臓が止まるような恋が　あること知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:09.01,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}会うたびに与えてくれた　憧れでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:16.31,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今でも信じている　もう消えることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:24.20,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ラクをせず　尽きることのない情熱は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:32.69,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どこから来るの？　どこかに眠っているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:40.46,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ララ　星が今運命を描くよ　無数の光輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:48.18,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今一つだけ決めたことがある　あなたとは離れない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:56.24,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そっと目を閉じれば　鼓動が聞こえる　私が生きてる証
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.50,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ハートの刻むリズムに乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:06.89,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}踊りながら行こう！　どこまでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:45.37,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ララ　星が今運命を描くよ　無数の光輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:53.02,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今一つだけ決めたことがある　あなたとは離れない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:19:01.13,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そっと目を閉じれば　鼓動が聞こえる　私が生きてる証
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:05.33,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ハートの刻むリズムに乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:12.22,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}踊りながら行こう！　どこまでも…
